name_en: Term: Proper Name or Product Name
definition_en: Proper names and products should not be used unless they are dominant to the point of being synonymous with a class of activity or a household name.
Youve identified an important term related to the stated topic, but the definition youve provided, while correct for other uses, is not correct for this topic.\n
Terms ought to be at a conceptual level. Terms that are specific to a specific implementation should generally be avoided.\n
The term was used to define itself.\n
